In the Matter of Glenda Connell, Appellant, v Board of Education of the City School District of the City of Utica, Respondent. (Appeal No. 2.)

Appeal unanimously dismissed, without costs (see Matter of Connell v Board of Educ. (106 AD2d 866). (Appeal from order of Supreme Court, Oneida County, Tenney, J. — reargue.) Present — Hancock, Jr., J. P., Doerr, Denman, Boomer and O’Donnell, JJ.
